### ============================================
### 7. CASOS DE ERROR
### ============================================

### 7.1 Obtener tipo de documento inexistente
# @name getNonExistent
GET {{baseUrl}}/document-types/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 📤 RESPUESTA ESPERADA (Error 404 Not Found):
### {
###   "success": false,
###   "status": "fail",
###   "message": "Tipo de documento con ID 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 no encontrado",
###   "code": "NOT_FOUND"
### }

### 7.2 Actualizar tipo de documento inexistente
# @name updateNonExistent
PUT {{baseUrl}}/document-types/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No existe"
}

